text: Well plov can be orange or purple
ok a taifel can be blue or yellow, either way it can have a big head and wings
a cheeba can be red or green
if it has a small head, it must have wings
kweps are usually large if orange but the other color can be small too
krivels always have small heads..they can have wings or no wings
javs can be either purple or red
feps can be any orange fish except the large one with whiskers. they can also be the green large one with whiskers
if they are large their stems will have spikes
a kaz can be large and red (no feathers) or small and red with feathers
stups are small with or without whiskers, only large green can be stup without whiskers
OR large, purple with feathers, or small purple without feathers
